(- A LEFT JOIN keeps every row from the left table, matched or not.) Tj
T*
(- A RIGHT JOIN keeps every row from the right table, matched or not.) Tj
T*
(- A FULL OUTER JOIN keeps unmatched rows from both sides, filling NULLs.) Tj
T*
(- Use LEFT JOIN whenever you must not lose rows from the primary table.) Tj
ET
endstream
